      <title>特斯拉股东在代理顾问的建议下拒绝马斯克的薪酬方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/tesla-shareholders-advised-by-iss-to-reject-musk-s-pay-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[代理顾问机构股东服务公司 (Institutional Shareholder Services) 敦促特斯拉公司股东拒绝首席执行官埃隆马斯克 (Elon Musk) 的 560 亿美元薪酬计划，这给这家电动汽车制造商的董事会设置了另一个障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/tesla-shareholders-advised-by-iss-to-reject-musk-s-pay-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 02:16:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联想与沙特的联盟提升了廉价人工智能相关股票的吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/lenovo-s-saudi-alliance-boosts-appeal-of-cheap-ai-related-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联想集团有限公司的股价可能继续跑赢同行，因为新兴市场的低估值和增长潜力吸引投资者投资这家中国电脑制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-31/lenovo-s-saudi-alliance-boosts-appeal-of-cheap-ai-related-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 May 2024 00:45:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达黄仁勋带领多位首席执行官参加台湾人工智能科技节</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/nvidia-amd-intel-qualcomm-arm-ceos-to-focus-on-ai-at-taiwan-s-computex</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司总裁黄仁勋将于本周日发表演讲，非正式地为 2024 年台北国际电脑展拉开序幕，这将是台湾年度电子产品展示活动有史以来规模最大的一次。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/nvidia-amd-intel-qualcomm-arm-ceos-to-focus-on-ai-at-taiwan-s-computex</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
