    <item>
      <title>人工智能服务器销量未能打动投资者，戴尔股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/dell-s-3-8-billion-ai-server-backlog-fails-to-impress-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[戴尔科技公司 (Dell Technologies Inc.) 在盘后交易中下跌约 18%，原因是其自 2022 年以来的首次营收增长不足以打动对该公司 AI 服务器业务寄予厚望的投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/dell-s-3-8-billion-ai-server-backlog-fails-to-impress-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 20:13:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果计划基于人工智能对 Siri 进行全面改造，以控制单个应用程序功能</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/apple-ios-18-siri-ai-update-will-let-users-control-features-in-apps-with-voice</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，苹果公司正计划以更先进的人工智能彻底改造其 Siri 虚拟助手，此举将允许用户通过语音控制单个应用程序的功能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/apple-ios-18-siri-ai-update-will-let-users-control-features-in-apps-with-voice</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 19:54:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国正在放缓 Nvidia、AMD 对中东的 AI 芯片出口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/us-officials-rein-in-ai-chip-sales-to-middle-east-by-nvidia-amd</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，美国官员已放缓向英伟达公司和超威半导体公司等芯片制造商发放向中东大规模出货人工智能加速器的许可证，同时对该地区人工智能发展进行国家安全审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/us-officials-rein-in-ai-chip-sales-to-middle-east-by-nvidia-amd</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 19:20:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前景不佳导致 Salesforce 股价暴跌 2008 年以来最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/salesforce-gives-weak-sales-outlook-with-slowdown-fears-growing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Salesforce Inc. 预计季度销售增幅将创历史新低，股价出现近 20 年来最大跌幅，这再次引发了人们对该公司将在人工智能热潮中落后的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/salesforce-gives-weak-sales-outlook-with-slowdown-fears-growing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 20:11:03 GMT</pubDate>
